(2^n+3^n+4^n)^{1/n}
n \rightarrow \infty?
4=(4^n)^{\frac1n}\leq (2^n+3^n+4^n)^{\frac1n}\leq (3\cdot4^n)^{\frac1n}=3^{\frac1n}\cdot4.
4\times((\frac2 4)^n+(\frac3 4)^n+1)^{\frac1n}
e=\lim_{n\to\infty}(1+\frac 1n)^n
n\frac{2^n+3^n}{4^n}\to 0
(1 + \frac{2^n+3^n}{4^n})^{\frac{4^n}{2^n+3^n}}\to e
4e^0=4
   (2^n+3^n+4^n)^{\frac 1n} ~ = ~~   4   \left(     1 + \frac{2^n+3^n}{4^n}   \right)^{n\frac{2^n+3^n}{4^n}\frac{4^n}{2^n+3^n}} 
